Elastic SIEM Alert Rule

Objective:
To detect brute-force login attempts automatically using alert thresholds.

Rule Configuration:
Rule Name: Detect 5+ Failed Logins in 5 Minutes
Index: security-login-*
Condition: Event count greater than 5 within 5 minutes

Testing Approach:
Simulated failed SSH login attempts were used to understand how such alerts would trigger in a real environment.
